lead_paragraph: Albania has moved Saturday's World Cup European Group G qualifier with Israel from the northern city of Shkoder to a venue near the capital Tirana due to security concerns, the Israeli Football Association said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Security Threat Prompts Albania to Relocate Match With Israel
